keyMappings:
# By default: <a-p> toggle pinning of tab
map # removeTab
map q removeTab
map <c-o> goBack
map <c-i> goForward
map [ previousTab
map ] nextTab
map u restoreTab
map g} moveTabToNewWindow
map gf nextFrame
map s LinkHints.activate action="focus"
map <c-e> passNextKey
map <c-y> switchFocus

exclusionRules.passKeys: # / ? a b c j k o r
